video_title: Why you must ALWAYS look for a purpose? #mindsetpodcast #motivation #inspiration
transcript:
if you don't know what your purpose is
that's fine right now but it is not okay
to not be in constant pursuit to find
that purpose every single day when we're
in sync with our purpose our actions
feel more effortless they feel like we
get energy from doing them and we feel
invigorated by the tasks that we have to
undertake
